summary: Electric harp cover of Skyrim theme.  Replaces Main Menu Music.
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the main menu music with a beautiful Skyrim theme cover.
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/qyIYq.jpg?1[/IMG]

\"Thank you from both of us for the mod. It is very cool. We appreciate? the work you did. Blessings, x2 <3 <3\"  -Camille and Kennerly

[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/D032j.gif[/IMG] [youtube]W5RB-gr9DTU[/youtube] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/D032j.gif[/IMG]

MY OTHER MODS:

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27425]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27425[/url]

If you also play Fallout New Vegas, go check out my mod \"Old World Radio\" here...

[url=http://newvegas.nexusmods.com/mods/47577]http://newvegas.nexusmods.com/mods/47577[/url]

It\'s the biggest radio mod to date.
